      <title>an attempt at a visual novel engine</title>
      <link>https://novelalex.com/an_attempt_at_a_vn_engine/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>novelalex29@outlook.com (Novel Alex)</author>
